615
00:24:41,660 --> 00:24:42,220
It's delicious.

616
00:24:42,780 --> 00:24:43,660
After you finish it,

617
00:24:43,780 --> 00:24:44,580
remember

618
00:24:44,740 --> 00:24:45,700
