669
00:27:30,460 --> 00:27:31,380
Who doesn't have that?

670
00:27:32,980 --> 00:27:34,620
The guy on your left.

671
00:27:34,980 --> 00:27:35,940
The short-haired fatty

672
00:27:36,220 --> 00:27:37,660
